Rules-Requires-Root: no

Package: libaprs0
Architecture: any
Multi-Arch: same
Section: libs
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Description: APRS packet parsing and transport library
 libaprs is a C library for parsing, building, and transporting APRS
 (Automatic Packet Reporting System) packets used in amateur radio.
 It provides layered support for TNC2 text, AX.25 UI frames, KISS
 framing, and APRS-IS connectivity.

Package: libaprs-dev
Architecture: any
Multi-Arch: same
Section: libdevel
Depends: libaprs0 (= ${binary:Version}), ${misc:Depends}
Description: APRS packet parsing and transport library (development files)
 libaprs is a C library for parsing, building, and transporting APRS
 (Automatic Packet Reporting System) packets used in amateur radio.
 .
 This package contains the header files and pkg-config file needed
 to build programs that use libaprs.
